Author: Yuxin Chen
Created: 09.2012
Description:  Implementation for the batch-mode active learning algorithm proposed in
	"Near-optimal batch mode active learning and adaptive submodular optimization", 
	Yuxin Chen and Andreas Krause, ICML'13.

File list: 
	main_active.m
	load_dataset.m
	batch_active.m
	hitandrun_sampler.m
	plot_samples.m
	out/
	+data/
	+data/+UCI/uci_australian_read.m
	+data/+UCI/uci_wdbc_read.m
	+data/+UCI/australian.doc
	+data/+UCI/australian.dat
	+data/+UCI/wdbc.names
	+data/+UCI/wdbc.data

Demo: 
	1. run main_active with default inputs for a demo of the batch-mode active learning algorithm.
	2. run hitandrun_sampler.m with default inputs for a demo of the noisy hit-and-run sampler